-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T15:49:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e43bb8c0965695ef39e07e6ae1a76f8b29d731f8","tid":1043140,"uid":54415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T16:03:46.000Z","msg":"聽講ALPHA佢改左條攻擊FORMULA同以前F個種唔同計法, 所以DAMAGE大好多, 冇實際研究過點計<br />\n不過實例係...真實系只改最強個招好容易打過萬DAMAGE, 高達系主角機一定得, 仲要個個有魂<br />\n超級系命中又唔計運動性, 平均命中率高唔少, 打卒都唔駛用必中<br />\n<br />\n到左外傳先難玩返少少, 第8關打真古蘭修, 高達係主角CUT魂, 隱藏機要低熟練兼搶BOX"},{"pid":"cceeb0252d5d31ce2eb5f59df27ea8d12bedc5c8","tid":1043140,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T11:58:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"352d42905cf345362a927235e30b4d2ea2a85116","tid":1043140,"uid":39369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:35:28.000Z","msg":"我淨係知alpha3後期打一關都要勁耐"},{"pid":"d50fca86d61ede53a3817601b1ff0c5bffc4ef41","tid":1043140,"uid":91931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"352d42905cf345362a927235e30b4d2ea2a85116","tid":1043140,"uid":39369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:35:28.000Z","msg":"我淨係知alpha3後期打一關都要勁耐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T16:39:27.000Z","msg":"嫌慢用伊迪安巾"},{"pid":"de8296ddd2f06a26fea6dac3cf77f41e90b5fa6e","tid":1043140,"uid":51566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T17:01:26.000Z","msg":"Alpha係第一隻有熟練度既game <br />\n好多關係開戰前後簡個option 已經會算熟練度 有d仲會+2/+3 咁 <br />\n印象三十幾關主角機都拎左新招 <br />\n加埋用其他勁機去打爆boss（50%血走） 應該唔難"},{"pid":"3a64daba11580432fde448219c329ae2a9b3c62d","tid":1043140,"uid":51566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"994c85e886d610ea32e99aff3c10457b62816f4d","tid":1043140,"uid":64191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T06:00:08.000Z","msg":"Alpha 4周目玩曬所有線，最難玩都係初期未齊戰力，但專心改幾部已經橫掃，0改就要稍微計距離移動<br />\n<br />\n話曬未有援攻援防，Alpha外傳敵人有援攻援防仲難打，又識得防禦回避，打Turn-X打到嗌救命"},"citedBy":1,"replyTim